data.description: 27 Acres! Wake up to a Hunter and Farmers Dream in a 4 Bedroom 3 1/2 Bath 2 Car oversized Garage with 2,800 sq ft of living space in Greene School District. This 1885 Farm House has been modernized with 2023 upgrades. You will be greeted to a long wide Foyer  which leads to a modern chef's kitchen, a double tiered breakfast bar, Counter top Range, and Double Ovens.  Perfect for entertaining a large party or family gathering. 10 foot ceilings lead you to the Open Concept a Formal Dining Room a Living Room with a Floor to Ceiling Flagstone Gas Fire Place. The 1st flr has a Family Rm, 1 Bedroom with a full bath,  Laundry Rm, and a 1/2 bath too. The 2nd Flr Master is Grand with a large Picture window and a walk out to an open deck. Master bath has a jacuzzi style tub. All bedrooms have wonderful views overlooking all that nature provides. Other listings include 90 acreage and barn and another 50 acres no barn.   Pasture, Hay field and woods. $10,000 carpet credit is being offered.
